text: Stade de Sibiti is a multi-use stadium in Sibiti, Republic of the Congo. The stadium holds 7,000 people. ==References== Category:Football venues in the Republic of the Congo Category:Athletics (track and field) venues in the Republic of the Congo Category:Sports venues in the Republic of the Congo Category:2014 establishments in the Republic of the Congo Category:Sports venues completed in 2014
